reviewText: I LOVE VINTAGE TELEVISION SHOWS, EVEN ONES THAT WERE HERE BEFORE I WAS BORN. I WAS FORTUNATE TO HAVE A MOTHER AND FATHER WHO PROVIDED A LOVING FAMILY HOME AND THE CLEAVERS, WHILE ONLY A T.V. FAMILY,  ARE REMINDERS OF HOW IT ONCE WAS.  WILL BE PURCHASING OTHER EPISODES, BUT THIS ONE IS A KEEPER.
you can never have too much leave it to beaver...the lunch box look case makes it a cute gift as well!
Received the sitcom quicker than expected. So happy my dad loves this show and gonna love it for Christmas.

Love these episodes.  I bought this and another Leave it to Beaver set for my kids to watch over the holiday break, now they love the series and want the others.  Such a great show to help teach the basics of life.
Nice, wholesome, family entertainment - brings back memories of years ago.

We love it !  Perfect condition
Includes  protective sponge  inside tin
Brand new
I might not have chosen the same 20 episodes as the best or a sampling of the total 250, but still they are enjoyable.
The video is very scratchy and a terrible picture! The tin case was also dented. This item was definitely not digitally remastered. Very disappointing.
Though I didn't grow up with "Leave It To Beaver," I really like its slow pace and being able to see what they thought was important in the 1950's.
